@startuml level4_hybrid
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 10

title **Level 4 — Hybrid Organization**\n//Hierarchical management + cross-agent iteration loops//

|#E3F2FD|Engagement Manager|
start
:Decompose & delegate;

fork
  |#E8F5E9|Market Researcher|
  :Market analysis;
fork again
  |#FFF3E0|Financial Analyst|
  :Financial analysis;
fork again
  |#FFEBEE|Risk Analyst|
  :Risk assessment;
end fork

|#E3F2FD|Engagement Manager|
:Review intermediate outputs;

if (EM approves?) then (yes)
  :Forward to Strategy Consultant;
else (no)
  :Request revisions\n(with feedback);
  backward :Specialists revise;
endif

|#F3E5F5|Strategy Consultant|
:Begin synthesis;

if (Needs more financial scenarios?) then (yes)
  |#FFF3E0|Financial Analyst|
  :Generate additional\nscenarios as requested;
  |#F3E5F5|Strategy Consultant|
  :Incorporate new data;
endif

if (Risk Analyst flags new issues\nrequiring market data?) then (yes)
  |#FFEBEE|Risk Analyst|
  :Flag issue to EM;
  |#E3F2FD|Engagement Manager|
  :Route request to\nMarket Researcher;
  |#E8F5E9|Market Researcher|
  :Provide supplementary\nmarket research;
  |#FFEBEE|Risk Analyst|
  :Update risk assessment;
  |#F3E5F5|Strategy Consultant|
  :Re-incorporate;
endif

|#F3E5F5|Strategy Consultant|
:Finalize consulting report;

|#E3F2FD|Engagement Manager|
:Final quality gate;

|#FFFDE7|Evaluator|
:Score on 6-criterion rubric;
stop

note right
  **Hybrid characteristics:**
  * Hierarchical control (EM reviews)
  * Cross-agent iteration loops
  * Risk Analyst → Market Researcher feedback
  * Strategy Consultant → Financial Analyst requests
  * Multiple rounds until quality sufficient
  * Highest quality, highest cost/time
end note

@enduml
